can sample the dipping sauce.

459
00:20:38,354 --> 00:20:40,820
Little tip:
avoid the Chinese mustard.

460
00:20:40,854 --> 00:20:43,782
Feels good going in,
not so good coming out.

461
00:20:44,438 --> 00:20:46,719
Let's just hope I find
her before I get old.

